''' Eravattur ''' is a [[village]] in [[Kozhikode district]] in the state of [[Kerala]], [[India]].<ref name="censusindia">{{cite web|url=http://www.censusindia.gov.in/Census_Data_2001/Village_Directory/Population_data/Population_5000_and_Above.aspx|title=Census of India : Villages with population 5000 & above|first=Registrar General & Census Commissioner, India|accessdate=2008-12-10}}</ref>

==Demographics==
[[As of 2001]] India [[census]], Eravattur had a population of 15716 with 7795 males and 7921 females.<ref name="censusindia" />

